not here to post any 2024 achievements. not here to tell you how everything on my vision board came true. 

just here to tell you that not all years are meant to be about achievements. some are meant for making mistakes, learning, healing, and growing. 2024 was that year for me. 

and in the end, i only have gratitude in my heart for all the lessons and love. 🥹💞

what do you wish for your 2025 to be like? for me the word of the year is going to be ABUNDANCE!!! tell me yours too 😚

shortest trip but the cutest memories 🥹🫶🏽
fun fact: i lived in bombay for a year in 2014 and that year propelled me into adulthood in every way possible. i had some of the worst experiences, but met some of the best people. i guess that’s bombay. 
life is so different (almost unrecognisable) 10 years later — but i wouldn’t have realised that had i not been back. so grateful for this tiny trip, but need to be back again soon to soak in more of this mumbaiya energy. ✨
